Package com.orchestranetworks.addon.adix

Classes and interfaces to call Adix import and export.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AdixExport Provides a method for executing an Adix export.
AdixImport Provides a method for executing an Adix import.
TransformContextForExport Provides methods for transforming data before exporting it to file.
TransformContextForImport Provides methods for transforming data before importing it into the repository.
Transformer Provides the methods for executing data transformation.
 

Class Summary
AdixExportResult Defines the results of an Adix export.
AdixExportSpec Defines an Adix export.
AdixFactory Factory for instances of AdixImport and AdixExport.
AdixImportResult Defines the results of an Adix import.
AdixImportResultBean Stores information after importing data into a table.
AdixImportSpec Defines an Adix import.
DataAccessSpec Defines data access specifications for Adix import and export.
ExportDataAccessSpec Defines the data access specifications for export.
ExportType This enumeration class defines the possible export types.
ImportDataAccessSpec Defines the data access specifications for import.
ImportType This enumeration class defines the possible import types.
TransformerCatalog Provides a list of transfomer classes to register.
TransformerDefinition This class contains methods that define attributes for Transformer implementations.
 

Exception Summary
AdixException Defines an Adix add-on exception.
